                  <summary>I) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” ["Ḥayq recension"](fols. 3ra-82vb)&#xD;
- Introduction (fols. 3r-7ra)&#xD;
- Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” ["Ḥayq recension"](fols. 7ra-82vb)&#xD;
II) Taʾāmra Takla Hāymānot “Miracles of ʾabuna Takla Haymanot” – 18 miracles (fols. 83ra-95ra)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
